node.text:
Man, I really wanted that second moto win but we just didn’t quite have it 😤. 3-2 for P3 OA to end the season. Made huge improvements these last three rounds to be up in the mix and where we belong. My hearts in it and I’m going to keep busting my ass towards next year to make sure I’m more than just an SX guy 😜. Thanks to my team, sponsors, and the fans. Let’s come out swinging and pack the fences again in ‘22! 

@ktmusa @ktmfactoryracing @redbull @redbullusa @thormxofficial @bellhelmets @100percent_moto @alpinestarsmx @paradiseautos @iamspecialized
